1
00:00:08,534 --> 00:00:11,626
Muhawe ikaze na none, iki ni 
igice cya nyuma muri iki cyumweru.

2
00:00:11,626 --> 00:00:13,394
Ndabashimira kuba mugeze kure bingana gutya!

3
00:00:13,395 --> 00:00:15,859
Iki cyumwer cyari 
icyo kwamamaza ibicuruzwa.

4
00:00:15,860 --> 00:00:20,217
Umukiriya ndetse n'abakeba
nibo twibanzeho muri iki cyumweru

5
00:00:20,218 --> 00:00:23,797
kubera ko ukeneye gusobanukirwa
iby'aba bakinnyi babiri bigenzi

6
00:00:23,798 --> 00:00:25,701
kugira ngo ubashe gucuruza.

7
00:00:25,702 --> 00:00:28,275
Kandi ndagirango wibuke
ijambo ry'ingenzi

8
00:00:28,276 --> 00:00:30,632
twabonye muri iki 
cyumweru by'umwihariko,

9
00:00:30,633 --> 00:00:32,750
akaba ari amagambo yavuzwe
na Peter Drucker wagize ati:

10
00:00:32,750 --> 00:00:35,189
"Intego y'ubucuruzi ni ukurema umukiriya,"

11
00:00:35,190 --> 00:00:37,619
ntabwo ari ukuremo igicuruzwa cyangwa
ikoranabuhanga bishya.

12
00:00:37,620 --> 00:00:40,376
Rero, nimucyo twongere turebe
ibyo twaganiye mu cyumweru gishize.

13
00:00:40,377 --> 00:00:42,353
Usibye ayo magambo, ndagirango mwibuke

14
00:00:42,354 --> 00:00:45,474
imbonerahamwe y'ingenzi 
twaganiriyeho tugitangira

15
00:00:45,475 --> 00:00:47,891
ndetse tunakanayinyuramo 
icyumweru cyose.

16
00:00:47,892 --> 00:00:50,277
Ni iyi mbonerahamwe ikwereka 

17
00:00:50,278 --> 00:00:54,402
uko kwamamaza mu bucuruzi 
bishobora gupangirwa mu mutwe wawe.

18
00:00:54,403 --> 00:00:56,597
Ibi ni bimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi

19
00:00:56,598 --> 00:00:58,878
ukeneye gusobanukirwa ku 
bucuruzi bwawe,

20
00:00:58,878 --> 00:01:01,677
ariwo mwihariko w'ikigo cyawe


21
00:01:01,677 --> 00:01:04,408
icyo urusha abandi

22
00:01:04,409 --> 00:01:07,701
ukaba ukigeraho bitewe
n'ubushobozi bwawe,

23
00:01:07,702 --> 00:01:10,295
kandi ni ngombwa kumenya

24
00:01:10,296 --> 00:01:13,557
ko hari ibyemezo bikomeye mu 
kwamamaza k'ubucuruzi,

25
00:01:13,557 --> 00:01:16,259
ibyemezo bijyanye n'imikorere
ndetse n'imitunganyirize

26
00:01:16,259 --> 00:01:17,469
uba ugomba gufata.

27
00:01:17,469 --> 00:01:20,488
Kandi iri tandukaniro ni ingenzi cyane,
nk'uko twabiganiye

28
00:01:20,489 --> 00:01:25,199
kuko gucamo ibice no gushyira ku murongo
ari ibyemezo by'ibanze

29
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:29,655
bizatangirira ndetse bikanategura 
ibindi byemezo byose

30
00:01:29,656 --> 00:01:31,851
uzigera ufata.

31
00:01:31,852 --> 00:01:34,851
Urugero, dufite ikorwa
ry'igicuruzwa/serivisi,

32
00:01:34,852 --> 00:01:36,911
guha izina ikigo cyawe, kugena 
ibiciro,

33
00:01:36,918 --> 00:01:39,579
gukwirakwiza ibicuruzwa, abakozi
bacuruza, guteza imbere ibicuruzwa,

34
00:01:39,580 --> 00:01:42,131
umubano na rubanda, ndetse no 
kwamamaza.

35
00:01:42,132 --> 00:01:45,194
Reka mbanyuze gato muri buri 
kimwe muri byo bintu byose --

36
00:01:45,195 --> 00:01:49,879
cyane cyane ibyemezo by'igihe kirekire,
ndetse n'ibyemezo by'ishyirwamubikorwa

37
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:51,535
ndetse n'amahitamo --
mu tudirishya dukeya.

38
00:01:51,536 --> 00:01:54,868
ibi byemezo by'igihe kirekire bijyanye,
nk'uko twamaze kubibona,

39
00:01:54,868 --> 00:01:57,035
no gucamo ibice ndetse no gushyira
mu mwanya,

40
00:01:57,035 --> 00:01:59,917
"Ese ni irihe(ayahe) soko(masoko) ngambiriye?"

41
00:01:59,918 --> 00:02:02,782
Akenshi, ba rwiyemezamirimo baba 
bafite isoko rimwe runaka bagambiriye.

42
00:02:02,782 --> 00:02:06,299
Ubwo ikibazo cyo gushyira ku mwanya kizaba:
"Kubera iki umuntu wo mu isoko (amasoko) ngambiriye

43
00:02:06,299 --> 00:02:09,297
azagura igicuruzwa cyangwa serivisi 
yanjye aho kugura ibya mukeba?"

44
00:02:09,298 --> 00:02:16,114
Uko rero ni ukuntu nzarebwa  n'abakiriya 
banjye ugereranyije na bakeba banjye.

45
00:02:16,114 --> 00:02:17,917
Ubusanzwe, nk'uko twabigaragaje,

46
00:02:17,918 --> 00:02:20,092
ibyo byemezo bifatirwa hamwe,

47
00:02:20,093 --> 00:02:22,854
kuko ushobora gutekereza ku
gace gato k'isoko ugamije

48
00:02:22,855 --> 00:02:27,249
maze ugahita ufata umwanzuro ngo: 
"Umwanya nshaka kugeraho

49
00:02:27,250 --> 00:02:30,136
ntabwo ujyanye n'aka gace,"
cyangwa se ubicuritse,

50
00:02:30,136 --> 00:02:34,029
rero iki mu kuri ni icyemezo rusange,
kandi ushobora kujya imbere n'inyuma

51
00:02:34,030 --> 00:02:36,569
kugeza igihe usobanukiwe mu
kuri isoko ryawe ugambiriye.

52
00:02:36,570 --> 00:02:41,984
kandi uko abantu, abakiriya,
ndetse n'isoko ugambiriye bazagufata

53
00:02:41,985 --> 00:02:43,735
ugereranyije na bakeba bawe.

54
00:02:43,736 --> 00:02:46,704
Icyingezi mu gusobanukirwa gucamo 
ibice no kwiha umwanya

55
00:02:46,705 --> 00:02:49,677
ni ugusobanukirwa abakiriya
bawe ndetse na bakeba bawe.

56
00:02:49,677 --> 00:02:52,128
Duhereye ku ruhande rw'abakiriya

57
00:02:52,129 --> 00:02:54,951
uribuka ko twaganiye ku nyungu

58
00:02:54,952 --> 00:02:59,241
igicuruzwa cyawe kiba gishobora 
guha abakiriya

59
00:02:59,242 --> 00:03:03,239
kubera ko abakiriya batagura ibiranga
ikintu, ahubwo bagura inyungu zacyo.

60
00:03:03,239 --> 00:03:05,948
Kandi ibi ni ingenzi cyane iyo bigeze
mu bintu by'ikoranabuhanga

61
00:03:05,948 --> 00:03:09,928
aho abantu bashukwa mu kuvuga go,
"Iki gicuruzwa kifite ibikiranga byiza."

62
00:03:09,929 --> 00:03:12,873
Umukiriya areba igicuruzwa
mu buryo bwo kuvuga ngo,

63
00:03:12,873 --> 00:03:14,979
"Ese iki kintu kimarira iki?

64
00:03:14,980 --> 00:03:17,771
Ni akahe kazi iki kintu
kinkorera?"

65
00:03:17,772 --> 00:03:21,968
Kugirango usobanukirwe abakiriya bawe
hari ibintu bibiri by'ingenzi,

66
00:03:21,969 --> 00:03:26,147
ibintu bibiri by'ibanze 
mu kurema ikigo gizakomera.

67
00:03:26,148 --> 00:03:29,813
Icya mbere, birumvikana, ni 
ugusobanukirwa abakiriya mbere yo kugurisha.

68
00:03:29,814 --> 00:03:33,102
Ibi bijyanye no gusobanukirwa 
ibyo abakiriya bakeneye

69
00:03:33,103 --> 00:03:35,300
Kandi twabivuzeho mu buryo burambuye.

70
00:03:35,301 --> 00:03:38,061
Icya kabiri, nacyo 
cy'ingenzi cyane

71
00:03:38,062 --> 00:03:41,238
kubera ko uba ukeneye kurema
umushinga mwiza ubyara agaciro,

72
00:03:41,238 --> 00:03:44,041
ni ugusobanukirwa abakiriya mu buryo
bwo kurema agaciro

73
00:03:44,041 --> 00:03:47,099
kuko abakiriya bose ntabwo
baguha agaciro kamwe.

74
00:03:47,099 --> 00:03:52,599
Gusobanukirwa ubwo bw'abakiriya 
buguha agaciro kurusha

75
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:55,467
bizagufasha kugaba igihe 
cyawe neza,

76
00:03:55,468 --> 00:03:58,891
cyane cyane ndetse n'imitungo 
ndetse n'ubushobozi bwawe.

77
00:03:58,892 --> 00:04:01,359
Naho ku bijyanye no gusobanukirwa
abakeba,

78
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:05,777
hari ibibazo bibiri twibanzeho
mu biganiro byacu:

79
00:04:05,778 --> 00:04:07,879
icya mbere cyari, "Bakeba bawe ni bande?"

80
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:11,931
icya kabiri cyari, "Ni iki twakenera 
kumenya kuri abo bakeba?"

81
00:04:11,932 --> 00:04:15,016
Akenshi, kandi ibyo ni nabyo
twaganiyeho,

82
00:04:15,017 --> 00:04:18,693
ba rwiyemezamirimo bakunda kuvuga ngo,
"Twazanye agashya,

83
00:04:18,693 --> 00:04:21,915
kandi kubera ko dufite agashya, ntidufite
abo duhanganye nabo."

84
00:04:21,915 --> 00:04:23,751
Ahubwo usanga akenshi icyo ari 
ikimenyetso

85
00:04:23,751 --> 00:04:28,637
ko rwiyemezamirimo adasobanukiwe
mu kuri bakeba be,

86
00:04:28,638 --> 00:04:30,053
yewe ndetse n'abakiriya be,

87
00:04:30,054 --> 00:04:34,188
kuko abakiriya akenshi bakora amahitamo
y'ibyo batakazaho amafaranga.

88
00:04:34,189 --> 00:04:38,625
Ubwo rero hari uguhangana nibura
ku mafaranga ari mu mifuka yabo.

89
00:04:38,625 --> 00:04:42,569
Ibishobora kuva muri ubu
bwo bwo gusesengura ni byinshi,

90
00:04:42,570 --> 00:04:44,540
gusa kugirango dusubiremo bimwe muri ibyo:

91
00:04:44,541 --> 00:04:48,122
icya mbere, ugomba gutuma
ibicuruzwa byawe bigira itandukaniro.

92
00:04:48,123 --> 00:04:49,852
Ugomba guha umwanya,

93
00:04:49,853 --> 00:04:52,392
gusobanukirwa aho ugomba gushyira ikigo cyawe.

94
00:04:52,392 --> 00:04:54,673
Ukeneye kandi gushyiraho
ibiciro byawe mu buryo bwiza

95
00:04:54,674 --> 00:04:58,401
kandi ukamenya ibyo ibigo muhanganye 
bishobora kugutwara.

96
00:04:58,402 --> 00:05:01,829
Hanyuma, birafasha gusobanukirwa neza
abo muhanganye,

97
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:06,088
birafasha gusobanukirwa mu kuri
aho ushobora kugeza ikigo cyawe.

98
00:05:06,089 --> 00:05:12,039
ibyo bigufasha kumenya ibyo usabwa mu bijyanye 
n'imitungo ndetse n'intego z'ibicuruzwa, n'ibindi.

99
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:14,835
Rero, iyo wamaze kureba
ibyo byose

100
00:05:14,836 --> 00:05:19,024
uba ufite ibikoresho byose byagufasha
gurema umushinga w'agaciro ufatika.

101
00:05:19,025 --> 00:05:22,254
Kandi twaganiye iby'ibirango by'
umushinga w'agaciro ufatika

102
00:05:22,255 --> 00:05:24,458
mu gace kamwe muri iki cyumweru.

103
00:05:24,459 --> 00:05:29,210
Mu magambo make, icyifuzo cy'
agaciro gishobora kuvuga mu nshamake

104
00:05:29,212 --> 00:05:33,036
muri izi nteruro imwe cyangwa ebyiri
muri kubona imbere yanjye hano.

105
00:05:33,037 --> 00:05:37,897
Interuro iravuga ngo, "Bitewe" n'ibikorwa
cyangwa ibicuruzwa na serivisi byacu

106
00:05:37,898 --> 00:05:40,991
"abakiriya" 
--uruzuzamo imyorondoro--

107
00:05:40,992 --> 00:05:44,348
"bari guhura" n'ubufasha runuka,

108
00:05:44,349 --> 00:05:48,240
ikibazo runaka,
cyangwa akababaro runaka,

109
00:05:48,241 --> 00:05:52,499
"bazabona" ikintu runaka
"ku" giciro runaka

110
00:05:52,500 --> 00:05:56,499
"ndetse bahabwe" inyungu
z'umukiriya cyangwa ubusubizwe runaka,

111
00:05:56,499 --> 00:05:59,335
mu gihe cyangwa bitarenze igihe runaka;

112
00:05:59,344 --> 00:06:02,738
maze ka kantu ko guhangana kakazom kavuga,

113
00:06:02,739 --> 00:06:04,976
"ugereranyije" n'aya moko y'ibindi bicuruzwa.

114
00:06:04,977 --> 00:06:07,999
"Ibyiza byo gukoresha ibintu 
turi gutanga ni" ibi, n'ibi, n'ibi.

115
00:06:07,999 --> 00:06:12,206
Muri iyo nteruro imwe gusa ushobora kugaragaza
mu nshamake

116
00:06:12,207 --> 00:06:14,642
ibyo ikigo cyawe kiri gutanga

117
00:06:14,643 --> 00:06:16,729
ndetse n'impamvu umukiriya
agomba kugura ibyo bintu

118
00:06:16,729 --> 00:06:18,921
aho kugura ibya mukeba.

119
00:06:18,922 --> 00:06:21,912
Iyi nteruro ushobora kumva yoroshye kuri 
wowe,

120
00:06:21,918 --> 00:06:25,210
ariko mu by'ukuri biragoye gutunganya
umugambi w'agaciro ufatika.

121
00:06:25,211 --> 00:06:26,701
Ariko ngushishikarije ibi ngibi

122
00:06:26,702 --> 00:06:31,692
kuko ukeneye kugira umucyo mu bwonko 
bwawe kucyo ikigo cyawe kiri gukora.

123
00:06:31,693 --> 00:06:35,222
Kandi uzibuke ibyo Drucker yavuze:
ikigo cyawe kigamije kurema umukiriya,

124
00:06:35,223 --> 00:06:37,544
ntabwo kigamije kurema igicuruzwa cyangwa
ikoranabuhanga.

125
00:06:37,545 --> 00:06:39,938
Muri iyi nteruro ugomba kumva 

126
00:06:39,939 --> 00:06:44,045
impamvu n'uburyo waremamo
umukiriya apana igicuruzwa.

127
00:06:44,046 --> 00:06:46,315
Noneho, tujya ku 
ruhande rw'ishyirwamubikorwa

128
00:06:46,316 --> 00:06:48,909
twaganiye ibintu bimwe na bimwe mu
rusange rwo kwamamaza.

129
00:06:48,909 --> 00:06:52,499
Wibuke ko hari igicuruzwa, igiciro,
ahantu, kwamamaza, uburyo,

130
00:06:52,501 --> 00:06:56,419
abantu; noneho ahantu hagukikije
ni akantu ka karindwi.

131
00:06:56,420 --> 00:07:01,311
Ushobora gutunganya ibyo bintu
mu buryo butondetse, igihe uzaba ufite

132
00:07:01,312 --> 00:07:04,926
ibyo byemezo by'igihe kirekiree
ku bijyanye no gucamo ibici no guha umwanya.

133
00:07:04,927 --> 00:07:07,215
Ibyo twabiganiyeho mu gice giheruka.

134
00:07:07,216 --> 00:07:09,870
Nk'uko ubyibuka, hari inzira ebyiri
nziza,

135
00:07:09,870 --> 00:07:13,113
inzira zidasanzwe z'ukuntu
ibigo bikivuka byiyamamaza.

136
00:07:13,125 --> 00:07:16,452
Twaganiye ku kwamamaza shuma
muri ubwo buryo, kuba akenshi

137
00:07:16,452 --> 00:07:20,558
ari ubwo bwo kwamamaza bujyanye n'
imirimo y'imenyekanisha

138
00:07:20,559 --> 00:07:23,204
ukorera mu rusange rwo kwamamaza.

139
00:07:23,205 --> 00:07:27,899
Twaganiye ingero nk'ebyiri 
zagufasha, ariko mu by'ukuri,

140
00:07:27,900 --> 00:07:32,337
ibyo watekereza mu bijyanye n'inzira nshya
zo kwamamaza igicuruzwa cyawe,

141
00:07:32,338 --> 00:07:34,983
ibijyanye no kwimenyekanisha ku bakiriya,

142
00:07:34,984 --> 00:07:37,527
aho igitekerezo kiba ri kimwe mu kuri
aho wakoresha igenamigambi rito

143
00:07:37,527 --> 00:07:41,096
ugakora ikintu gikomeye mu bijyanye 
n'uburyo ukurura abantu

144
00:07:41,097 --> 00:07:43,500
ku kigo ndetse n'bicuruzwa byawe.

145
00:07:43,501 --> 00:07:46,495
Ubwo rero igihe twavugaga ku bijyanye
no kwamamaza shuma, twanavuze

146
00:07:46,495 --> 00:07:50,272
ko uburyo ukora uko kwamamaza shuma,
ndetse n'ishyirwamubikorwa

147
00:07:50,273 --> 00:07:52,917
biba akenshi bifitanye isano 
n'ibikorwa byawe byo kwimenyekanisha,

148
00:07:52,918 --> 00:07:57,012
ariko, birumvikana, ibi bigomba kuba bifitanye 
isano n'umwanya wahaye ikigo cyawe

149
00:07:57,013 --> 00:08:02,625
ndetse n'icyo igice ugamije gucuruzaho 
gikunda mu by'ukuri kubona ku kigo cyawe.

150
00:08:03,250 --> 00:08:07,417
Ntugatuke igice ugambiriye ngo uri gukoresha
ubwoko bwa gisazi bwo kwamamaza shuma

151
00:08:07,418 --> 00:08:10,082
kuko ibyo bishobora kukugiraho
ingaruka mbi cyane

152
00:08:10,083 --> 00:08:12,575
niba wifuzaga gukora ikigo cy'imari gikomeye.

153
00:08:12,576 --> 00:08:15,654
iki kandi, twavuze ku kuntu gukusanya amafaranga 
muri rubanda ari igikoresho cyo kwamamaza.

154
00:08:15,655 --> 00:08:19,623
Mwibuke ko tuzagaruka kuri iki kiganiro
mu cyumweru gitaha

155
00:08:19,624 --> 00:08:22,413
ubwo tuzaba tuganira ku gukusanya amafaranga
muri rubanda nk'igikoresho cyo kwamamaza,

156
00:08:22,414 --> 00:08:24,028
ariko mu rwego rwo kwamamaa,

157
00:08:24,028 --> 00:08:26,547
gukusanya amafaranga muri rubanda bifite 
ibintu byiza cyane nka bibiri.

158
00:08:26,548 --> 00:08:29,913
Kandi, nk'uko ushobora kuba ubyibuka, bigufasha 
gupima no kwemeza isoko ryawe,

159
00:08:29,913 --> 00:08:32,921
kugaragaza ibitekerezo byawe,
kugenzura imyitwarire y'abashoramari.

160
00:08:32,922 --> 00:08:35,756
bigufasha kubaka urutonde rw' "abagushyigikiye"

161
00:08:35,756 --> 00:08:38,880
ndetse no kubaka imibano n'
abashobora kuba abakiriya.

162
00:08:38,881 --> 00:08:41,629
Binagufasha kumenyekanisha izina ryawe,

163
00:08:41,629 --> 00:08:44,030
ndetse bwa nyuma, kuzamura iterambere
ndetse no gutanga igabanya ry'ibiciro

164
00:08:44,030 --> 00:08:46,839
ku bicuruzwa bishya cyanwa binsaznwe
urimo uratunganya.

165
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:52,658
Imiryango yo gukusanya amafaranga muri rubanda
ari mu by'ukuri gutanga inyungu nyinshi zitari iz'ubukungu

166
00:08:52,659 --> 00:08:56,680
kandi ibyo abantu benshi ntibabyitaho,
rero ntekereza ko ari ingenzi

167
00:08:56,681 --> 00:08:58,908
ko ujya mu mirimo
nk'iyi ngiyi

168
00:08:58,909 --> 00:09:00,648
kugirango utangire umushinga wawe.

169
00:09:00,649 --> 00:09:04,616
Twanaganiye kandi ku bindi bintu bibiri:
gukoresha ikoranabuhanga n'ubuhinga bw'imikurire.

170
00:09:04,617 --> 00:09:08,270
Gukoresha ikoranabuhanga: wibuke cya kiciro
cy'ikoreshwa ry'ikoranabuhanga,

171
00:09:08,271 --> 00:09:11,791
cyane cyane akantu kamwe kari ingenzi


172
00:09:11,792 --> 00:09:13,832
ariko gitekerezo cyo gusimbuka icyobo.

173
00:09:13,832 --> 00:09:18,457
Wibuke ko twari dufite icyobo
hagati y'abarikoresheje bwa mbere

174
00:09:18,458 --> 00:09:21,749
ndetse n'abenshi mu bantu bagize
agace kagambiriwe.

175
00:09:21,750 --> 00:09:26,141
Wibuke ko kandi abo bantu batandukaniye
mu buryo bakira ibintu

176
00:09:26,142 --> 00:09:29,017
ndetse n'bushake bwo 
kugura ibicuruzwa bifite udushya.

177
00:09:29,018 --> 00:09:32,964
Hanyuma aho umutego akenshi uba uri:

178
00:09:32,965 --> 00:09:35,297
hagati y'abakoresheje ikoranabuhanga bwa mbere
n'abantu benshi b'icyo gihe.

179
00:09:35,298 --> 00:09:38,609
Harimo umutego muri ubu buryo:

180
00:09:38,626 --> 00:09:43,868
wowe nka rwiyemezamirimo ugize
ibicuruzwa bya mbere, uri kugera ku ntego,

181
00:09:43,869 --> 00:09:46,556
ubwo rero icyo abenshi bumva bakora
ni ukongeramo andi mafaranga

182
00:09:46,557 --> 00:09:51,502
mu gukore igicuruzwa cyawe, mu 
kwamamaza, n'ibindi.

183
00:09:52,853 --> 00:09:55,508
Ariko wirengagije mu by'ukuri
igice gikurikira

184
00:09:55,508 --> 00:09:58,211
uzaba ukeneneye kumvisha:
rubanda nyamwinshi rwa mbere,

185
00:09:58,212 --> 00:10:01,043
aho uzahera ubona amafaranga menshi.

186
00:10:01,044 --> 00:10:03,543
Icyo gice kigura ku mpamvu zitandukanye.

187
00:10:03,543 --> 00:10:06,552
Rero uzibuke ko kugira ngo
usimbuke urwo rwobo

188
00:10:06,553 --> 00:10:08,570
ugomba guhindura ubutumwa
bwawe bwo kwamamaza,

189
00:10:08,570 --> 00:10:11,154
ugomba guhindura uburyo
ugezamo ubutumwa ku bakiriya,

190
00:10:11,154 --> 00:10:16,260
ubwoko bw'izindi serivisi zijyanye 
ushobora kuzabaha, n'ibindi.

191
00:10:16,261 --> 00:10:20,115
Noneho bwa nyuma, twaganiye ku
ku kuntu wagera ku iterambere rirambye.

192
00:10:20,116 --> 00:10:23,267
Iyi birumvikana ko ari imwe mu ntego 
z'ibanza ba rwiyemerazamirimo bose bagira,

193
00:10:23,267 --> 00:10:26,446
kandi ni na kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi
bigize kwamamaza mu by'ubucuruzi.

194
00:10:26,446 --> 00:10:28,685
Kugira ngo usobanukirwe uburyo
wagera ku iterambere,

195
00:10:28,686 --> 00:10:31,496
ugomba gusobanukirwa ibijyanye
no gutunganya umushinga wawe

196
00:10:31,497 --> 00:10:33,324
imikurire yawo,

197
00:10:33,324 --> 00:10:36,906
kandi ugomba no gusobanukirwa
uko uzihutisha imikurire

198
00:10:36,906 --> 00:10:39,031
binyuze mu kwibanda cyane ku 
mikurire.

199
00:10:39,031 --> 00:10:42,057
Ubwo rero ushobora kureba ku rusange
rw'ibintu bigize ukwamamaza twabonye

200
00:10:42,058 --> 00:10:45,360
mu buryo bugufasha gukura,

201
00:10:45,361 --> 00:10:49,828
ndetse ukanagerageza gutunganya ibyo bintu 
mu buryo bugufasha gukura.

202
00:10:49,828 --> 00:10:53,834
Akenshi ibyo ni byo muri iyi minsi
bita ubuhinga bw'imikurire.

203
00:10:53,838 --> 00:10:55,930
Ubwo ushobora no gutekereza ku nzira z'ubuhanga

204
00:10:55,931 --> 00:10:58,449
wakoresha urire umunyengo ku mikurire
y'ibindi bigo by'ubucuruzi.

205
00:10:58,449 --> 00:11:01,481
Twarebeye hamwe zimwe mu ngero z'ibi 
ngibi nanone.

206
00:11:01,482 --> 00:11:05,744
Ibi rero bituzanye ku musozo w'
Icyumweru cya 3 -- igihe kiraguruka koko.

207
00:11:05,745 --> 00:11:09,537
Icyi cyari Icyumweru cya 3
gifite kwamamaza mu bucuruzi

208
00:11:09,538 --> 00:11:11,440
nk'insanganyamatsiko y'ingenzi, nkuko
nari nabivuze.

209
00:11:11,441 --> 00:11:15,731
Muri iki cyumweru twize ibintu 
by'ingenzi bibiri,

210
00:11:15,732 --> 00:11:18,025
uburyo wasobanukirwa
kwamamaza mu bucuruzi.

211
00:11:18,026 --> 00:11:20,999
Umurimo wo kwamamaza n'ingenzi cyane 
ku kigo cyawe cy'ubucuruzi,

212
00:11:20,999 --> 00:11:23,252
Ubwo rero ugomba kuwitondera,

213
00:11:23,253 --> 00:11:27,139
wite ku buryo utegura kwamamaza kwawe
mu buryo bufite akamaro kenshi gashoboka,

214
00:11:27,140 --> 00:11:30,593
kandi uzanite ku buyo
bishyirwa mu bikorwa.

215
00:11:30,594 --> 00:11:32,586
Amahirwe masa rero no kwamamaza kwawe.

216
00:11:32,586 --> 00:11:33,942
Tuzongere tubonane.
